Ground with Knowledge
Select the title, summary, and additional knowledge fields for Einstein to ground on. Required editions: Enterprise and Unlimited Editions with the Einstein for Service add-on.

Required Fields:
Title Field and Summary Field.
Additional Fields:
Any other fields you want Einstein to consider for grounding.
Save and Activate grounding for your Knowledge records.
Einstein begins indexing your published Knowledge Articles.

IMPORTANT
Field level security limits the grounded responses that users can see. Users only see grounded responses for fields they can access.
Users only see grounded responses for Knowledge Article Versions they can access.
Encrypted fields aren’t supported for grounding.
